    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ON_CHANGE

        public static final PersistPolicy ON_CHANGE
        Save persistence storage on each change. This mode is safe because in case the application dies it has persistence storage saved. Drawback is a performance hit.

      • ON_EXIT

        public static final PersistPolicy ON_EXIT
        Saves persistence storage on method PersistStorage.shutdown() call.
